  <h2>Run your first simulation</h2>
  <p class="lead">
    Python 3.10+. Offline mock works immediately; Ollama and OpenRouter are
    optional for real dialogues.
  </p>

  <pre class="pre"><span class="comment"># install</span>
pip install -e ".[dev]"

<span class="comment"># offline smoke test — no LLM</span>
python examples/hello_world.py

<span class="comment"># local LLM</span>
ollama pull llama3.2:3b
python examples/ollama_simple.py

<span class="comment"># live dashboard</span>
uvicorn server.main:app --port 8000</pre>
